targets.rawSql:
SELECT insee_section,count(*) AS nb
FROM wda_sirene_etablissements
WHERE insee_section_id IN (${section:sqlstring})
GROUP BY insee_section
ORDER BY nb DESC

SELECT insee_division,count(*) AS nb
FROM wda_sirene_etablissements
WHERE insee_division_id IN (${division:sqlstring})
GROUP BY insee_division
ORDER BY nb DESC

SELECT insee_groupe,count(*) AS nb
FROM wda_sirene_etablissements
WHERE insee_groupe_id IN (${groupe:sqlstring})
GROUP BY insee_groupe
ORDER BY nb DESC

SELECT insee_classe,count(*) AS nb
FROM wda_sirene_etablissements
WHERE insee_classe_id IN (${classe:sqlstring})
GROUP BY insee_classe
ORDER BY nb DESC

SELECT insee_sous_classe,count(*) AS nb
FROM wda_sirene_etablissements
WHERE insee_classe_id IN (${classe:sqlstring})
GROUP BY insee_sous_classe
ORDER BY nb DESC

SELECT ets_departementetablissement,count(*) AS nb
FROM wda_sirene_etablissements
WHERE insee_sous_classe_id IN (${sousclasse:sqlstring}) AND ets_minnbeffectifsetablissement IN (${effectif:sqlstring}) AND ets_departementetablissement in (${departement:sqlstring})
GROUP BY ets_departementetablissement
ORDER BY nb DESC

SELECT ets_geonames_city,count(*) AS nb
FROM wda_sirene_etablissements
WHERE insee_sous_classe_id IN (${sousclasse:sqlstring}) AND ets_minnbeffectifsetablissement IN (${effectif:sqlstring}) AND ets_departementetablissement IN (${departement:sqlstring}) AND ets_geonames_city IN (${ville:sqlstring})
GROUP BY ets_geonames_city
ORDER BY nb DESC

SELECT ets_siret,ets_siren,ets_datecreationetablissement,ets_etablissementsiege,ets_minnbeffectifsetablissement,ets_numerovoieetablissement,ets_typevoieetablissement, ets_libellevoieetablissement,ets_codepostaletablissement,ets_departementetablissement,ets_geonames_city,ets_enseigne1etablissement,ets_enseigne2etablissement,ets_enseigne3etablissement,ets_denominationusuelleetablissement,insee_sous_classe
FROM wda_sirene_etablissements
WHERE insee_sous_classe_id IN (${sousclasse:sqlstring}) AND ets_minnbeffectifsetablissement IN (${effectif:sqlstring}) AND ets_departementetablissement IN (${departement:sqlstring}) AND ets_geonames_city IN (${ville:sqlstring})

SELECT ets_siret,ets_siren,ets_datecreationetablissement,ets_etablissementsiege,ens_denominationUniteLegale, ens_denominationUsuelle1UniteLegale, ets_denominationusuelleetablissement, ets_minnbeffectifsetablissement,ets_numerovoieetablissement,ets_typevoieetablissement, ets_libellevoieetablissement,ets_codepostaletablissement,ets_departementetablissement,ets_geonames_city,ets_enseigne1etablissement,ets_enseigne2etablissement,ets_enseigne3etablissement,insee_sous_classe,ets_latitude,ets_longitude
FROM wda_sirene_etablissements
WHERE insee_sous_classe_id IN (${sousclasse:sqlstring}) AND ets_minnbeffectifsetablissement IN (${effectif:sqlstring}) AND ets_departementetablissement IN (${departement:sqlstring}) AND ets_geonames_city IN (${ville:sqlstring})
